votingLinks.bannerMessage:
Reminder that the polls will remain open until February 8, 2024. Given the long voting period, we highly encourage you to thoroughly think about what you are voting for and to not rush it, especially if you only watched few of the anime nominated. You can bookmark this page for now if you still need more time.

Though each one has a freedom on how they want to vote, we highly encourage diversifying one's choices and avoid "straight ticket" voting.

IMPORTANT NOTE: Per our existing rules, any Fall 2023 Anime that are still airing this Winter 2024 had their nominations transferred or reserved for next year instead.

votingLinks.bannerMessage:
Reminder that the polls will remain open until February 8, 2024. Given the long voting period, we highly encourage you to thoroughly think about what you are voting for and to not rush it, especially if you only watched few of the anime nominated. You can bookmark this page for now if you still need more time.

Though each one has a freedom on how they want to vote, we highly encourage diversifying one's choices and avoid "straight ticket" voting.

IMPORTANT NOTE: Per our existing rules, any Fall 2023 Anime that are still airing this Winter 2024 had their nominations transferred or reserved for next year instead.
